HEADWORD: Cobblestone
<hw>Cob"ble*stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A large pebble;
a rounded stone not too large to be handled; a small boulder; -- used
for paving streets and for other purposes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cobby</ent>⟦br⟧
